Subject: Re: [T2] starter motor troubles

Check all the battery cable connections all along the way to the starter,
grounds, grounds between trans and engine etc etc, I would be willing to bet
it's not getting enough voltage to crank properly. Corrosion can do this at
the starter connections.
HTH,
Courtney

 
